author: Corridor Crew
description:
Did you notice something strange in the flying shots of James Gunn's Superman? Well, if you did, you were not crazy.

Jordan explains why David Corenswet used a bald cap for the flying shots, which gave birth to the infamous Bald Superman photo you might have seen on social media.

Did you find his flying believable?
title: Did you know SUPERMAN was actually BALD?!
